            "title": "Late Quaternary (MIS 5a-5b) climate and environments of western Iberia inferred from the small-mammal assemblage of Gruta da Oliveira, Torres Novas, Portugal",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Juan Manuel",
                    "lastName": "López-García"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
