            "title": "Bat remains (Mammalia, Chiroptera) from the Middle Pleistocene site of Qesem Cave, Israel, with the first Pleistocene record of fruit bats in the Mediterranean region",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "I",
                    "lastName": "Horáček"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
